content: Hey, I am Cole, a software engineering intern at Intuit. I will be completeing my BSc. in Fall 2019. My interests include information retrieval, cloud computing, big data, backend development, and service reliability. I currently have 2 years of work experience at Intuit across 3 different teams. I have helped develop backend services and tools for Optical Character Recognition, Call Center Technology, and Data Lake processing.
